    "headline": "Metazoa Announces Updates to Snapshot on Salesforce AppExchange",
    "summary": "SAN FRANCISCO, April 06, 2026--Metazoa introduces an AI assistant for Salesforce that analyzes metadata and takes action to manage complexity, reduce risk, and improve org health.",
    "url": "https://finance.yahoo.com/sectors/technology/articles/metazoa-announces-updates-snapshot-salesforce-120000923.html",
