        "contentType": "STORY",
        "title": "Metazoa Announces Updates to Snapshot on Salesforce AppExchange",
        "description": "",
        "summary": "SAN FRANCISCO, April 06, 2026--Metazoa introduces an AI assistant for Salesforce that analyzes metadata and takes action to manage complexity, reduce risk, and improve org health.",
        "pubDate": "2026-04-06T12:00:00Z",
        "displayTime": "2026-04-06T12:00:00Z",
        "isHosted": true,
        "bypassModal": false,
        "previewUrl": null,
        "thumbnail": {
          "originalUrl": "https://media.zenfs.com/en/business-wire.com/c7778d373cd13b5b20f139ed65104d97",
          "originalWidth": 1920,
          "originalHeight": 1080,
          "caption": "Metazoa today introduced the Intelligent Assistant for Snapshot, a new way to manage and transform Salesforce orgs with AI. As org complexity grows, teams face increasing challenges with visibility, technical debt, and maintaining agility. Most AI tools can identify problems. The Metazoa Intelligent Assistant goes further by helping teams fix them. Operating within full org context, it can inspect metadata, launch reports, analyze dependencies, generate documentation, and guide remediation in real time. Users can switch between Admin, Architect, and Developer perspectives to take action with the right context. This is Total Org Intelligence for Salesforce—AI that moves beyond analysis to execution, enabling organizations to transform faster and operate with confidence. Find Anything. Fix Everything.",
          "resolutions": [
            {
              "url": "https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/d5N5lhjE7q7Y.Nxd9ZEdIQ--~B/aD0xMDgwO3c9MTkyMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/business-wire.com/c7778d373cd13b5b20f139ed65104d97.cf.webp",
